en:
Come and meet our local producers!

For this visit, you will be welcomed at the Brewen Microbrewery by Pierre Yves GUENOLE, producer of organic, local and committed beers!
He will take you behind the scenes of the production process and explain the different steps from the small hop seed, or rather the multitude of seeds, that he chooses among the varieties coming from the Champ du Houblon in Bourgneuf en Retz (44), a few dozen kilometers from Saint-Brevin, to the elaboration of the drink.

He will tell you about his strong commitments: organically grown products, a manufacturing process that favors recycling and reuse while limiting water consumption, the Brewen microbrewery is resolutely oriented towards a circular economy.
At the end of the visit, you will taste one of its blond, red or amber beers...

Please note: Beer tastings are exclusively reserved for adults. Alcohol abuse is dangerous.



